did.unittitle: Department of Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University, reference service records

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records include research applications; correspondence; guides; donor files; registration forms; files of Thomas Rossiter Barnum; master microforms of the Stimson Papers index and catalog; call slips; ofice of origin request forms; reprographics order forms; and other files concerning reference activities of the Department of Manuscripts and Archives at Yale University Library. The records include the correspondence of the curator of Yale Memorabilia (1907-1933).

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by type of material and in subsequent accessions.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records include research applications; correspondence; guides; donor files; registration forms; files of Thomas Rossiter Barnum; master microforms of the Stimson Papers index and catalog; call slips; ofice of origin request forms; reprographics order forms; and other files concerning reference activities of the Department of Manuscripts and Archives at Yale University Library. The records include the correspondence of the curator of Yale Memorabilia (1907-1933).
